1268
01:45:49,968 --> 01:45:55,332
So we do have an acoustician that we work with as part of our consultant team on the design of every project.

1269
01:45:55,432 --> 01:46:02,317
And those types of adjacencies are something that we focus sort of an initial acoustic report on on every project.

1270
01:46:02,357 --> 01:46:05,499
And they review our documents as we go along through the process.

1271
01:46:05,899 --> 01:46:14,045
