1272
01:46:14,405 --> 01:46:16,447
You have to build a lot of mass into those walls.

1273
01:46:16,467 --> 01:46:19,509
You have to build a lot of acoustic isolation into those walls as well.

1274
01:46:19,969 --> 01:46:26,334
You also have to think vertically if there's spaces below, spaces above that are potentially going to receive the noise.

1275
01:46:26,374 --> 01:46:34,100
So it's not easy and it's not cheap in terms of making those types of isolations possible, but it is possible.

1276
01:46:34,160 --> 01:46:36,342
